{
  "texts": [
    "Study Selection and Eligibility CriteriaAll the articles that matched our search criteria were double-screened by two independent reviewers (ZG, KL) to ensure each article fell within the scope of LLMs in mental health.",
    "This process involved the removal of duplicates followed by a detailed manual evaluation of each article to confirm adherence to our predefined inclusion criteria, ensuring a comprehensive and focused review.",
    "To quantify the agreement level between the reviewers and ensure objectivity, inter-rater reliability was calculated using Cohen's kappa, with a score of 0.84 indicating a good level of agreement.",
    "In instances of disagreement, a third reviewer (AL) was consulted to achieve consensus.To assess the risk of bias, we utilized the Risk of Bias 2 tool, as recommended for Cochrane Reviews.",
    "The results have been visualized in Multimedia Appendix 1."
  ]
}